= SDL_RWFromFP =
Use this function to create [[SDL_RWops]] structures from a standard I/O file pointer.


== Syntax ==
```c++
SDL_RWops* SDL_RWFromFP(FILE*    fp,
                        SDL_bool autoclose)
```

